            <thetext>If you are using qx.ui.table.columnmodel.Resize as column model, every column count calls _updateAllRows() on qx.ui.explorer.pane.Pane

There is no queue for this elemental function, so on every column size computing all rows will be updated. 

A queue job could be helpful for performance issues.</thetext>
